-- U.S. to announce criminal charges against SAC Capital on Thursday: source
-- 
-- Wed Jul 24, 2013 5:07pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/07/24/us-sac-insider-thursday-idUSBRE96N1BK20130724

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - U.S. prosecutors are planning to announce criminal charges on Thursday against Steven A. Cohen's hedge fund SAC Capital Advisors, a source familiar with the matter said on Wednesday. 
 The charges will be wire fraud and securities fraud, according to the source. A spokesman for the Federal Bureau of Investigation declined to comment. A spokeswoman for U.S. Attorney Preet Bharara declined to comment. A spokesman for SAC Capital declined to comment. (Reporting By Matthew Goldstein)